scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Pieces included: 1 score, flute part, clarinet in b-flat part, bass trombone part, vibraphone and triangle part, CD, program note.. Notes: Lyrics written by Emily Dickenson. submission letter housed with Menageríe. Note on envelope: ZM1.1 .01, ZM1.2 .02.
